101
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:22,480
would you tell him

102
00:07:23,200 --> 00:07:25,040
that you once wanted to kill him?

103
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:33,440
I would definitely not tell.

104
00:07:33,760 --> 00:07:35,480
Since we are now so close,

105
00:07:35,760 --> 00:07:36,920
why bother doing so

106
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:37,960
to ruin the relationship?

107
00:07:42,760 --> 00:07:43,560
No, no.

108
00:07:45,960 --> 00:07:46,760
Annoying!

109
00:07:48,200 --> 00:07:48,880
Annoying!

110
00:07:48,880 --> 00:07:49,680
Get to sleep.

111
