114
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:25,480
with my cunning and villainous
younger brother.

115
00:08:27,360 --> 00:08:29,080
She had the smell of herbal medicine

116
00:08:29,880 --> 00:08:31,200
the last time she broke into
the Demon Palace.

117
00:08:33,760 --> 00:08:35,920
She must have been ordered

118
00:08:35,920 --> 00:08:37,280
by my younger brother to kill me.

119
00:08:37,880 --> 00:08:39,280
