123
00:08:44,040 --> 00:08:45,800
an explanation, don't you?

124
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:50,600
No one would ever do so.

125
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:54,640
I can't believe she lied to me.

126
00:08:56,400 --> 00:08:58,000
I'd better keep away from her.

127
00:09:10,760 --> 00:09:11,440
My Lord.

128
00:09:11,560 --> 00:09:13,280
Are you not feeling well?

129
00:09:13,280 --> 00:09:14,000
Exactly.

130
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:15,240
I am not

131
00:09:15,240 --> 00:09:16,440
