134
00:09:18,640 --> 00:09:19,160
My Lord.

135
00:09:19,160 --> 00:09:20,480
Shall I ask General Hua to come?

136
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:22,080
Don't!

137
00:09:22,560 --> 00:09:23,680
Don't mention her.

138
00:09:23,680 --> 00:09:24,520
And don't let me see her.

139
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:25,640
Once you mention her,

140
00:09:25,640 --> 00:09:26,840
my heart would flutter.

141
00:09:30,160 --> 00:09:31,200
If she asks,

142
00:09:31,800 --> 00:09:33,280
just say that I am not well.

143
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:34,960
I don't meet anyone these days.

144
00:09:36,560 --> 00:09:37,360
Oh.

145
00:09:43,400 --> 00:09:45,280
His heart flutters for General Hua.

146
00:09:51,120 --> 00:09:52,160
Miss Jinli.

147
00:09:54,240 --> 00:09:55,360
Please return.

148
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:56,640
The Lord is not feeling well.

149
00:09:56,760 --> 00:09:57,280
Today,

150
00:09:57,520 --> 00:09:58,640
