151
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:02,600
Mr. Yu.

152
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:04,080
I am not a visitor.

153
00:10:04,920 --> 00:10:06,440
I am here on behalf of General Hua

154
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:09,280
