162
00:10:24,120 --> 00:10:25,400
However,

163
00:10:29,040 --> 00:10:30,640
the Lord reigns over the Demon Realm,

164
00:10:30,800 --> 00:10:32,240
but when facing with love,

165
00:10:32,520 --> 00:10:33,680
he would be worried.

166
00:10:33,880 --> 00:10:34,960
Please ask General Hua

167
00:10:35,120 --> 00:10:36,440
to forgive him.

168
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:38,040
L...

169
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:39,640
Love?

170
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:41,760
Miss Jinli.

171
00:10:41,920 --> 00:10:44,120
