194
00:11:56,560 --> 00:11:57,080
No!

195
00:11:57,080 --> 00:11:57,880
Please protect me.

196
00:12:04,560 --> 00:12:05,120
General.

197
00:12:06,440 --> 00:12:07,560
What happened to your face?

198
00:12:07,560 --> 00:12:08,360
Nothing.

199
00:12:13,200 --> 00:12:15,240
