for the first time.

200
00:12:17,000 --> 00:12:17,800
Does he

201
00:12:18,920 --> 00:12:20,520
really have a crush on me?

202
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:36,640
Boring.

203
00:12:39,200 --> 00:12:39,960
My Lord.

204
00:12:40,080 --> 00:12:42,360
I understand you.

205
00:12:44,280 --> 00:12:45,080
You understand?

206
00:12:46,640 --> 00:12:49,080
Are you really struggling now?

207
00:12:53,440 --> 00:12:56,240
Do you not know how to face her?

208
00:13:01,400 --> 00:13:02,840
Are you getting uneasy

209
00:13:02,840 --> 00:13:04,880
whenever you think of her?

210
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:07,040
Exactly.

211
00:13:07,360 --> 00:13:08,120
