amidst the amassed pebbles?♪

252
00:14:47,670 --> 00:14:50,270
♪In mediocrity, we comfort each other♪

253
00:14:50,270 --> 00:14:53,040
♪Fortunate to have you with me♪

254
00:14:53,040 --> 00:14:54,660
♪Holding the blazing heat♪

255
00:14:54,660 --> 00:14:58,130
♪Still singing the song
that belongs to us♪

256
00:14:58,130 --> 00:15:00,790
♪If there are no more
starry rivers ahead♪

257
00:15:00,880 --> 00:15:02,320
♪Then let's become fireflies♪

258
00:15:02,320 --> 00:15:05,490
♪Tiny lights illuminating
our dwelling place♪

259
00:15:05,590 --> 00:15:08,340
♪Welcoming all creations as guests♪

260
00:15:08,340 --> 00:15:11,510
♪Our singing constructs
immortality and persistence♪

261
00:15:11,750 --> 00:15:14,100
♪We've lived madly in our time♪

262
00:15:14,330 --> 00:15:17,000
♪Don't fear making
the same mistakes again♪

263
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:18,420
♪Wandering and displaced♪

264
00:15:18,730 --> 00:15:23,670
